<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2008-12-19.S3W-18668.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-08/wa1219.htm#8">Justice</minor-heading>

<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2008-12-19.S3W-18668.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80291" speakername="Robert Brown (Glasgow) (LD)" spid="S3W-18668" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-08/wa1219.htm#8">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive how many CCTV cameras there were in each of the last 10 years, broken down by local authority.</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2008-12-19.S3W-18668.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80306" speakername="Fergus Ewing" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-08/wa1219.htm#8">

  <p>No central records have been kept of this data over the last 10 years. No instruction has been given by the Scottish Government for this data to be so held.</p>

  <p>The strategic review of public space CCTV in Scotland, which is expected to conclude shortly, will include a landscaping element which would provide us with the figures for public space only CCTV in Scotland covering a single year.</p>

</reply>


<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2008-12-19.S3W-18669.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-08/wa1219.htm#8">Justice</minor-heading>

<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2008-12-19.S3W-18669.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80291" speakername="Robert Brown (Glasgow) (LD)" spid="S3W-18669" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-08/wa1219.htm#8">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive how regularly on average a CCTV camera requires to be replaced.</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2008-12-19.S3W-18669.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80306" speakername="Fergus Ewing" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-08/wa1219.htm#8">

